---
import Navigation from "~/components/Navigation/Navigation.astro";

import "./styles/style.scss";
---

<Navigation />
<main>
  <section class="about is-visible" id="about">
    <div class="about__content">
      <h2 class="heading" data-heading="about">About Me</h2>
      <div class="about__content__info" data-description="about">
        <div class="about__content__portret">
          <div class="border"></div>
          <img src="../static/assets/portret.jpg" alt="myself" class="img" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-info">
          Hello! My name is Peter. I'm 20 years old and I enjoy creating
          websites and applications.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="about__content__text" data-description="about">
        My programming adventure started from february 2021 year. I learn new
        things quickly and try to do everything precisely. I improve my skills
        every day and I'm having a lot of fun with it. I'm very motivated to
        learn more and gain experience.
      </p>
      <p class="about__content__text" data-description="about">
        In my spare time from coding, I have been training in the gym for about
        5 years. I am a calm, patient person who strives to achieve its goals.
      </p>
      <p class="about__content__text" data-description="about">
        If you wanna know more about me write me <a
          href="#contact"
          data-href="contact">contact</a
        >
      </p>
      <p class="about__content__text" data-description="about">
        Here are some of the technologies I have worked with up to this moment:
      </p>

      <div class="about__content__skill" data-description="about">
        <div class="about__content__skill-container">
          <p class="about__content__skill-heading">Front-end:</p>
          <ul class="about__content__skill-list">
            <li>React</li>
            <li>Gatsby</li>
            <li>Next</li>
            <li>Astro</li>
            <li>Redux / Zustand</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>Three.js (WebGl)</li>
            <li>Jest / RTL</li>
            <li>Styled-components</li>
            <li>Tailwind</li>
            <li>Css modules</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about__content__skill-container" data-description="about">
          <p class="about__content__skill-heading">Back-end:</p>
          <ul class="about__content__skill-list">
            <li>Express</li>
            <li>Firebase</li>
            <li>Mongodb</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <canvas class="canvas-about" data-canvas="about"></canvas>
  </section>
</main>
